Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:28.40,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I was born normal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:33.28,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I become normal, can I stay close?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:38.77,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}With the children, we link our arms
